race.comment: Tough and the resumers may hold the key. SHAMROCK BAY (3) resumes and is right up to this if on song. Has placed 2/4 fresh and won a recent jumpout at the track. Trained here and has run some nice races in stronger. REBILLYOUS (2) also rates well at best and has placed 2/4 fresh as well. Jumps from an inside gate and Newitt replaces Jennings who sticks with the above. SLEEPING TIGER (8) has been within range his last three in stronger. Fit and can't be ruled out in this lineup. THE CRUISER (6) resumes and would be a hope at best. He went okay here two back and may have had an issue at Bairnsdale when last seen.
